WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.489 --> 00:00:13.339
Welcome to Ahmet's kitchen, today we will be making vegetarian Bulgur with beans

00:00:13.339 --> 00:00:19.730
Sunflower oil

00:00:19.730 --> 00:00:25.829
a bit of butter

00:00:25.829 --> 00:00:32.829
about 30g, the onions

00:00:46.350 --> 00:00:53.350
3 onions

00:00:54.500 --> 00:01:01.500
add in here

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:32.700
2 peppers

00:01:32.700 --> 00:01:37.020
one sweet and one hot

00:01:37.020 --> 00:01:38.260
cut into small pieces

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:56.760
let the onions roast

00:02:04.030 --> 00:02:09.599
they need about 3 minutes

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.879
now clean the peppers

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:18.879
stir

00:02:21.979 --> 00:02:28.979
in oil pickled tomatoes, take a few pieces out

00:02:36.349 --> 00:02:38.929
5 pieces

00:02:38.929 --> 00:02:45.929
cut into small pieces

00:02:50.609 --> 00:02:55.859
another one

00:02:57.589 --> 00:03:02.919
add in here

00:03:31.969 --> 00:03:34.469
2 min

00:03:34.469 --> 00:03:36.359
roast the tomatoes a little

00:03:36.359 --> 00:03:37.909
and peppers

00:03:42.709 --> 00:03:45.279
now tomato paste

00:03:45.279 --> 00:03:52.279
a spoon

00:03:53.479 --> 00:04:00.479
stir

00:04:04.989 --> 00:04:07.069
now the bulgur

00:04:07.069 --> 00:04:10.079
300g

00:04:24.159 --> 00:04:31.159
stir

00:04:40.879 --> 00:04:43.819
Now the beans

00:04:43.819 --> 00:04:48.050
washed out of the can

00:04:48.050 --> 00:04:53.949
and then put it in

00:04:53.949 --> 00:04:55.479
now add

00:04:55.479 --> 00:05:01.699
a spoonful of vegetable broth

00:05:02.830 --> 00:05:06.779
a spoonful of chicken broth (accidentally added)

00:05:06.779 --> 00:05:08.740
Mexican

00:05:08.740 --> 00:05:10.069
with chili, a spoon

00:05:10.069 --> 00:05:17.069
pepper

00:05:19.059 --> 00:05:21.039
and salt

00:05:21.039 --> 00:05:28.039
Half a liter of water, we will see how much we need later, stir

00:05:52.770 --> 00:05:59.770
OK

00:06:01.659 --> 00:06:05.039
cover the pan

00:06:07.259 --> 00:06:09.319
turn the stove down

00:06:09.319 --> 00:06:11.379
not too much

00:06:11.379 --> 00:06:16.169
4 of 9

00:06:17.860 --> 00:06:19.119
Bulgur is finished after 30 min

00:06:20.979 --> 00:06:24.869
we added 600ml water

00:06:24.869 --> 00:06:31.869
let's take a look

00:06:31.900 --> 00:06:38.860
stir again

00:06:38.860 --> 00:06:40.849
distribute

00:06:40.849 --> 00:06:43.220
cover it again

00:06:49.289 --> 00:06:51.469
Let it stand for 10 min

00:06:51.469 --> 00:06:56.520
then you can eat it with salad or Cacik to

00:06:56.520 --> 00:06:57.520
until next time, Ahmet, bye :)

